---
layout: "base"
title: "Bipolare Störung – Psychoedukation für Angehörige | PUK Zürich"
description: "Als Angehörige*r bei bipolarer Störung: 8 fundierte Module für Orientierung, Entlastung und konkrete Schritte. Notfallhilfe und interaktive Tools. PUK Zürich."
permalink: "/"
noJs: true
navCurrent: "home"
navShowSub: true
useSharedCSS: true
useNavJS: true
---
{% block headCSS %}
<style>
  /* ══════════ HERO ══════════ */
  .home-hero {
    min-height: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 2rem 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .home-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 800px;
    height: 800px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(141, 212, 217, 0.72) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.88;
  }

  .home-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10%;
    left: -5%;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(221, 210, 191, 0.95) 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.82;
  }

  .home-hero-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 24px auto 24px 0;
    width: min(560px, 100%);
    border-radius: 34px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.94), rgba(247,242,234,0.74));
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(28,43,58,0.09);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .home-hero-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .home-hero-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(320px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .home-hero-text {
    max-width: 620px;
    padding: 26px 30px 26px 0;
  }

  .home-hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(28,43,58,0.92);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .home-hero-badge::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sand);
  }

  .home-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--earth-900);
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .home-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .home-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .home-hero-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    min-height: 46px;
    padding: 0 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--teal));
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-elevated);
  }

  .home-hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 18px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .home-hero-meta p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .home-hero-meta strong {
    color: var(--earth-900);
  }

  .home-hero-emergency-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    width: fit-content;
    min-height: 40px;
    padding: 0 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: rgba(199,84,80,0.1);
    color: var(--alert-red);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .home-hero-visual-card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(243,229,225,0.48));
    border: 1px solid rgba(181,138,82,0.14);
    border-radius: 26px;
    padding: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(28,43,58,0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .home-hero-visual {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 18px;
  }

  /* ══════════ SECTION GENERIC ══════════ */
  section {
    padding: 80px 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--sage-500);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--earth-900);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* ══════════ PROGRESS BAR ══════════ */
  .progress-section {
    padding: 0 2rem 40px;
  }

  .progress-section.is-empty {
    display: none;
  }

  .progress-bar-outer {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 18px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .progress-label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .progress-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--sage-100);
    border-radius: 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 0%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--sage-400), var(--sage-500));
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: width 0.6s ease;
  }

  .progress-count {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sage-600);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .orientation-shell {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.14fr) minmax(280px, 0.86fr);
    gap: 22px;
    align-items: start;
    margin: 34px 0 26px;
  }

  .entry-layout {
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .entry-list {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #fcf8f4 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 24px 26px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .entry-list-kicker {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-500);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .entry-list-intro {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    max-width: 48ch;
  }

  .entry-clarifier {
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(247,242,234,0.94) 0%, rgba(217,236,236,0.42) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06);
  }

  .entry-guidance-kicker {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sand-ink);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .entry-clarifier p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  .entry-clarifier p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .entry-clarifier strong {
    color: var(--earth-900);
  }

  /* ══════════ MODULE GRID ══════════ */
  .modules-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .urgent-note {
    display: block;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .urgent-note {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--alert-red-bg), rgba(255,255,255,0.98));
    border: 1px solid var(--alert-red-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 24px 26px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .urgent-note-kicker {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--alert-red);
  }

  .urgent-note p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .urgent-note-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    width: fit-content;
    min-height: 40px;
    padding: 0 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: rgba(199,84,80,0.12);
    color: var(--alert-red);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .choice-note {
    margin-top: 22px;
    max-width: 860px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,#fff 0%,#fbf7f0 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .choice-note strong {
    color: var(--earth-900);
  }

  .choice-note a {
    color: var(--sage-600);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .orientation-shell .start-helper,
  .orientation-shell .urgent-note {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .entry-secondary {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .entry-details-stack {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .entry-details {
    border-radius: 22px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,#fff 0%,#fcf8f4 100%);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .entry-details summary {
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .entry-details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .entry-details summary::after {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    right: 20px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--sage-600);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .entry-details[open] summary::after {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    background: var(--sage-500);
    color: white;
  }

  .entry-details-kicker {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-500);
  }

  .entry-details-title {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 1.16rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--earth-900);
    padding-right: 44px;
  }

  .entry-details-body {
    padding: 0 22px 18px;
  }

  .modules-grid--situational {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .module-card--situational {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 18px 0;
    box-shadow: none;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .module-card--situational:hover {
    box-shadow: none;
    border-color: rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
  }

  .module-card--situational:first-child {
    border-top: none;
  }

  .module-card--situational .module-number {
    color: var(--sand-ink);
  }

  .module-card--situational h3 {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .module-card--situational p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    max-width: 58ch;
  }

  .module-card--situational .module-card-footer {
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .module-card--situational .module-arrow {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
  }

  .modules-grid--roles {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .module-card--role {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #fcf8f4 100%);
    border-color: rgba(181,138,82,0.14);
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .module-card--role:hover {
    border-color: rgba(30,101,109,0.18);
  }

  .role-card {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .role-starts {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.05);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .role-starts-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-500);
  }

  .role-start-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .role-start-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 34px;
    padding: 0 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .role-start-link:hover {
    border-color: rgba(30,101,109,0.22);
    background: var(--green-bg);
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .module-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .module-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    border-color: var(--sage-200);
  }

  .module-number {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--sage-400);
  }

  .module-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--earth-800);
  }

  .module-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .module-card-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.05);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .module-time {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .module-arrow {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--sage-50);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--sage-500);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .module-card:hover .module-arrow {
    background: var(--sage-500);
    color: white;
  }

  /* ══════════ DECORATIVE DIVIDER ══════════ */
  .wave-divider {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    line-height: 0;
    margin: -1px 0;
  }

  .wave-divider svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 60px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ══════════ CTA BAND ══════════ */
  .cta-band {
    background: var(--sage-700);
    padding: 60px 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-band::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(141,156,115,0.3) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-band h2 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .cta-band p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--sage-700);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
  }

  /* ══════════ FOOTER ══════════ */
  

  

  .footer-brand h3 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .footer-brand p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .footer-col h4 {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .footer-col a {
    display: block;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 4px 0;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .footer-col a:hover { color: white; }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 40px auto 0;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }

  .footer-bottom a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-left: 20px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .footer-bottom a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

  /* ══════════ SCROLL REVEAL ══════════ */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px);
    transition: opacity 0.55s ease, transform 0.55s ease;
  }
  .reveal.revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; }
    .reveal.revealed { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }
  /* Fallback: show all content if JS is disabled */
  .no-js .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

  /* ══════════ VISITED MODULE BADGE ══════════ */
  .module-card.visited .module-arrow {
    background: var(--sage-500);
    color: white;
  }
  .module-card.visited {
    border-color: var(--sage-200);
  }

  /* ══════════ MOBILE NAV ══════════ */
  

  

  /* ══════════ RESPONSIVE ══════════ */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .home-hero-content::before { inset: 12px 0 auto 0; width: 100%; height: 320px; }
    .home-hero-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 26px; }
    .home-hero-text { padding: 18px 0 0; }
    .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; text-align: center; }
    .modules-grid--roles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .orientation-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }


  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .home-hero { padding: 110px 1.2rem 60px; min-height: auto; }
    .home-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .home-hero-visual-card { display: none; }
    .progress-section { padding: 0 1.2rem 26px; }
    .progress-label { white-space: normal; text-align: center; }
    .start-helper { margin: 22px 0 28px; padding: 20px 18px; }
    .urgent-note { padding: 20px 18px; }
    section { padding: 50px 1.2rem; }
    .modules-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .progress-bar-outer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    .cta-band { padding: 50px 1.2rem; }
    .entry-list,
    .entry-clarifier,
    .entry-details summary,
    .entry-details-body { padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px; }
    
  }

  /* ══════════ PATH LIST (Startwege) ══════════ */
  .path-list{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0}
  .path-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;padding:16px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06)}
  .path-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .path-num{flex-shrink:0;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--sage-100);color:var(--teal);font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-top:2px}
  .path-body{flex:1}
  .path-title{font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);font-size:0.95rem;margin:0 0 4px;text-decoration:none;display:block}
  .path-title:hover{color:var(--teal)}
  .path-desc{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--slate);margin:0;line-height:1.5}

  /* ══════════ STARTHELFER ══════════ */
  .start-helper{margin:28px 0 36px;padding:24px 26px;border-radius:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fff 0%,#fcf8f4 100%);border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06);box-shadow:var(--shadow-soft)}
  .start-helper-kicker{font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage-500);margin-bottom:10px}
  .start-helper h3{font-family:'Source Serif 4',serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin:0 0 8px}
  .start-helper p{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 18px}
  .start-helper-options{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px}
  .start-helper-option{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;width:100%;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:16px;border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.08);background:#fff;color:var(--text);text-align:left;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s ease,box-shadow 0.2s ease,transform 0.2s ease}
  .start-helper-option:hover{border-color:var(--sage-200);box-shadow:var(--shadow-soft);transform:translateY(-1px)}
  .start-helper-option.is-active{border-color:var(--teal);background:var(--green-bg)}
  .start-helper-icon{min-width:74px;height:34px;padding:0 10px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(221,210,191,0.3);color:var(--sand-ink);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:none}
  .start-helper-option.is-active .start-helper-icon{background:var(--teal);color:#fff}
  .start-helper-label{display:block;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:3px}
  .start-helper-sub{display:block;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.45}
  .start-helper-result{margin-top:16px;padding:18px 20px;border-radius:18px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-warm) 0%,rgba(217,236,236,0.42) 100%);border:1px solid rgba(45,40,35,0.06)}
  .start-helper-result[hidden]{display:none}
  .start-helper-result-kicker{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--slate);margin-bottom:8px}
  .start-helper-result h4{font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin:0 0 6px}
  .start-helper-result p{font-size:0.86rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0 0 12px}
  .start-helper-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;text-decoration:none;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--teal));padding:10px 16px;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.84rem;font-weight:700}
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .start-helper-options{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

  /* ══════════ QUICK TRIAGE ══════════ */
  .quick-triage{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--rose-soft),#fff8f6);border:1px solid rgba(154,52,18,0.12);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:24px}
  .quick-triage-label{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--rose);margin-bottom:12px}
  .quick-triage h3{font-family:'Source Serif 4',serif;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px}
  .quick-triage p{font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6}
  .triage-question{margin-bottom:16px}
  .triage-question[hidden]{display:none}
  .triage-q-text{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.45}
  .triage-btns{display:flex;gap:10px}
  .triage-btn{padding:10px 24px;border-radius:10px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.2s,color 0.2s;border:none}
  .triage-btn--yes{background:var(--rose);color:#fff}
  .triage-btn--yes:hover{background:#7f1d1d}
  .triage-btn--no{background:rgba(45,40,35,0.06);color:var(--text-secondary)}
  .triage-btn--no:hover{background:rgba(45,40,35,0.1)}
  .triage-result{padding:16px 20px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);margin-top:12px}
  .triage-result[hidden]{display:none}
  .triage-result a{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;text-decoration:none;color:#fff;background:var(--rose);padding:10px 20px;border-radius:999px}
  .triage-result--safe{background:var(--green-bg);border:1px solid rgba(13,122,95,0.15);padding:14px 20px;border-radius:var(--radius-md)}
  .triage-result--safe p{font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--green-phase);margin:0}
  .triage-result--safe a{background:none;padding:0;color:var(--teal);text-decoration:underline;font-size:inherit;border-radius:0;display:inline}

  /* ══════════ TOOLS HIGHLIGHT ══════════ */
  .tools-highlight{margin:48px auto;max-width:var(--content-width-wide);padding:0 2rem}
  .tools-highlight-label{font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:12px}
  .tools-highlight h2{font-family:'Source Serif 4',serif;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px}
  .tools-highlight > p{font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:20px;max-width:48ch}
  .tools-highlight-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
  .tool-highlight-card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f0fafa,#fff);border:1px solid rgba(30,101,109,0.12);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:20px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--navy);transition:box-shadow 0.2s,transform 0.2s}
  .tool-highlight-card:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow-card);transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .tool-highlight-icon{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:1rem}
  .tool-highlight-card h3{font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
  .tool-highlight-card p{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.45;margin:0}
  .tool-highlight-all{text-align:center;margin-top:14px}
  .tool-highlight-all a{font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal);text-decoration:none}
  .tool-highlight-all a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
  @media(max-width:768px){.tools-highlight-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  @media(max-width:480px){.tools-highlight-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
{% endblock %}
{% block nav %}
{% include "nav-full.njk" %}
{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
<header class="home-hero">
  <div class="home-hero-content">
    <div class="home-hero-body">
      <div class="home-hero-text">
        <div class="home-hero-badge">Psychiatrische Universitätsklinik Zürich · Fachstelle Angehörigenarbeit</div>
        <h1>Als Angehörige*r von Menschen mit <em>bipolarer Störung</em></h1>
        <p class="home-hero-subtitle">Sie müssen hier nicht alles auf einmal verstehen. Diese Website hilft Ihnen, Ihre Lage einzuordnen und den Einstieg zu wählen, der im Moment am ehesten passt.</p>
        <a href="#orientierung" class="home-hero-link">Zur Orientierung ↓</a>
        <div class="home-hero-meta">
          <p><strong>Für Partner*innen, Eltern, Geschwister und erwachsene Kinder.</strong> Sie dürfen hier von Ihrer eigenen Lage ausgehen, nicht nur von der erkrankten Person.</p>
          <a href="/notfall/" class="home-hero-emergency-link">Wenn es akut sein könnte: direkt zum Notfallweg</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="home-hero-visual-card">
          <picture>
            <source type="image/webp" srcset="/visuals/home-editorial-hero-v3-web.webp 1280w, /visuals/home-editorial-hero-v3.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 42vw">
            <img src="/visuals/home-editorial-hero-v3-web.png" srcset="/visuals/home-editorial-hero-v3-web.png 1280w, /visuals/home-editorial-hero-v3.png 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 42vw" alt="Ruhige editoriale Illustration von drei erwachsenen Angehörigen in einem häuslichen Gesprächs- und Unterstützungsmoment." class="home-hero-visual" width="1536" height="1024" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high">
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main-content">

<!-- ══════════ PROGRESS ══════════ -->
<div class="progress-section" id="progressSection">
  <div class="progress-bar-outer">
    <span class="progress-label">Ihr Fortschritt</span>
    <div class="progress-track">
      <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
    </div>
    <span class="progress-count" id="progressCount">0 / 8 Module</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════ TRIAGE ══════════ -->
<section id="orientierung">
  <div class="section-label reveal">Orientierung</div>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">Wo stehen Sie gerade?</h2>
  <p class="section-desc reveal">Sie müssen nicht linear durch die Website gehen. Beginnen Sie mit der Frage, was <strong>jetzt</strong> am meisten drängt: Gefahr, Verstehen, eigene Erschöpfung oder konkrete Unterstützung. <strong>Ein Einstieg reicht.</strong></p>

  <div class="quick-triage reveal" id="quickTriage">
    <div class="quick-triage-label">Schnelleinordnung</div>
    <h3>Was passiert gerade?</h3>
    <p>Drei kurze Fragen helfen Ihnen, den richtigen Einstieg zu finden.</p>
    <div class="triage-question" id="triageQ1">
      <div class="triage-q-text">Besteht gerade Gefahr für Leib und Leben?</div>
      <div class="triage-btns">
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--yes" data-triage="q1-yes">Ja oder unklar</button>
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--no" data-triage="q1-no">Nein</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="triage-question" id="triageQ2" hidden>
      <div class="triage-q-text">Sind Sie selbst gerade am Limit — erschöpft, überfordert, ausgebrannt?</div>
      <div class="triage-btns">
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--yes" data-triage="q2-yes">Ja</button>
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--no" data-triage="q2-no">Nein</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="triage-question" id="triageQ3" hidden>
      <div class="triage-q-text">Brauchen Sie vor allem Grundlagenwissen über die Erkrankung?</div>
      <div class="triage-btns">
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--yes" data-triage="q3-yes">Ja</button>
        <button type="button" class="triage-btn triage-btn--no" data-triage="q3-no">Nein, eher Werkzeuge und Orientierung</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="triage-result" id="triageResult" hidden aria-live="polite"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="orientation-shell">
    <div class="start-helper reveal" aria-labelledby="start-helper-title">
      <div class="start-helper-kicker">Starthelfer</div>
      <h3 id="start-helper-title">Was brauchen Sie gerade am ehesten?</h3>
      <p>Wählen Sie das, was Ihrer Lage im Moment am nächsten kommt. Sie bekommen direkt einen sinnvollen ersten Einstieg. Mehr müssen Sie jetzt nicht entscheiden.</p>
      <div class="start-helper-options" role="group" aria-label="Starthelfer: Einstieg auswählen">
        <button type="button" class="start-helper-option" data-start-helper="akut" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="startHelperResult">
          <span class="start-helper-icon" aria-hidden="true">Akut</span>
          <span><span class="start-helper-label">Akut / unklar gefährlich</span><span class="start-helper-sub">Ich muss zuerst klären, ob Gefahr besteht.</span></span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="start-helper-option" data-start-helper="verstehen" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="startHelperResult">
          <span class="start-helper-icon" aria-hidden="true">Wissen</span>
          <span><span class="start-helper-label">Einordnen und verstehen</span><span class="start-helper-sub">Ich brauche zuerst Überblick und Grundlagen.</span></span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="start-helper-option" data-start-helper="erschoepft" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="startHelperResult">
          <span class="start-helper-icon" aria-hidden="true">Entlastung</span>
          <span><span class="start-helper-label">Ich bin erschöpft</span><span class="start-helper-sub">Meine eigene Belastung steht gerade im Vordergrund.</span></span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="start-helper-option" data-start-helper="hilfe" aria-pressed="false" aria-controls="startHelperResult">
          <span class="start-helper-icon" aria-hidden="true">Hilfe</span>
          <span><span class="start-helper-label">Kontakte / Materialien / Recht</span><span class="start-helper-sub">Ich brauche jetzt Orientierung, Anlaufstellen oder praktische Unterstützung.</span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="start-helper-result" id="startHelperResult" hidden aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true">
        <div class="start-helper-result-kicker">Empfohlener Einstieg</div>
        <h4 id="startHelperTitle"></h4>
        <p id="startHelperText"></p>
        <a id="startHelperLink" class="start-helper-link" href="/">Empfohlenen Einstieg öffnen →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="urgent-note reveal" aria-label="Akuter Einstieg">
      <div class="urgent-note-kicker">Wenn Sie zuerst Gefahr klären müssen</div>
      <p>Bei Suizidgedanken, Manie, Psychose, Gewalt oder finanzieller Eskalation ist der Notfallweg wichtiger als jede weitere Sortierung. Nutzen Sie ihn sofort.</p>
      <a href="/notfall/" class="urgent-note-link">Direkt zum Notfallweg →</a>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <div class="entry-layout">
    <div class="entry-list reveal">
      <div class="entry-list-kicker">Situative Einstiege</div>
      <p class="entry-list-intro">Wenn es nicht akut ist, wählen Sie den Weg, der Ihrer eigenen Lage gerade am nächsten kommt. Das ist die ruhigste Art, hier einzusteigen.</p>
      <div class="modules-grid modules-grid--situational">
        <a href="/modul/1/" class="module-card module-card--situational">
      <span class="module-number">Verstehen</span>
      <h3>Ich muss erst einordnen, was hier überhaupt passiert</h3>
      <p>Wenn Sie Verhalten, Phasen, Behandlung und schwer lesbare Verläufe besser verstehen wollen, bevor Sie weitergehen.</p>
      <div class="module-card-footer">
        <span class="module-time">Modul 1</span>
        <span class="module-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>

        <a href="/modul/4/" class="module-card module-card--situational">
      <span class="module-number">Belastung</span>
      <h3>Ich merke, dass ich selbst seit Langem mittrage</h3>
      <p>Wenn Erschöpfung, Anspannung, Rückzug oder das Gefühl im Vordergrund stehen, schon zu lange durchzuhalten.</p>
      <div class="module-card-footer">
        <span class="module-time">Modul 4</span>
        <span class="module-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>

        <a href="/modul/3/" class="module-card module-card--situational">
      <span class="module-number">Beziehung</span>
      <h3>Unsere Beziehung fühlt sich nicht mehr wie Beziehung an</h3>
      <p>Wenn Rollen sich verschoben haben, Vertrauen brüchig geworden ist oder Nähe und Leichtigkeit fehlen.</p>
      <div class="module-card-footer">
        <span class="module-time">Modul 3</span>
        <span class="module-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>

        <a href="/modul/5/" class="module-card module-card--situational">
      <span class="module-number">Dilemma</span>
      <h3>Ich schwanke zwischen Dableiben und Selbstschutz</h3>
      <p>Wenn Schuld, Wut, Grenzstress oder die Frage nach Abstand, Bleiben oder Neuordnung drängen.</p>
      <div class="module-card-footer">
        <span class="module-time">Modul 5</span>
        <span class="module-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </a>

        <a href="/modul/8/" class="module-card module-card--situational">
      <span class="module-number">Hilfe</span>
      <h3>Ich suche Anlaufstellen, Downloads oder konkrete Unterstützung</h3>
      <p>Wenn Sie jetzt vor allem Kontakte, Materialien oder rechtliche Orientierung brauchen. Für Gespräche, Grenzen und Krisenplan passt eher Modul 6.</p>
      <div class="module-card-footer">
        <span class="module-time">Modul 8</span>
        <span class="module-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="entry-clarifier reveal">
    <div class="entry-guidance-kicker">Für den Moment reicht ein Weg</div>
    <p><strong>Modul 6</strong> ist der passendere Einstieg für Gespräche, Grenzen und Krisenplan.</p>
    <p><strong>Modul 8</strong> ist meist hilfreicher, wenn Sie Kontakte, Materialien oder rechtliche Orientierung suchen.</p>
    <p>Die geordneten Startvorschläge und die Rollen-Orientierung sind unten nur als optionale Vertiefung für später aufgeklappt.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════ OPTIONAL LATER ══════════ -->
<section class="entry-secondary">
  <div class="section-label reveal">Optional für später</div>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">Wenn Sie geordneter weiterlesen oder nach Ihrer Rolle schauen möchten</h2>
  <p class="section-desc reveal">Die erste Orientierung oben reicht völlig. Die beiden Aufklappbereiche hier sind nur für später: für Menschen, die lieber systematisch lesen oder ihre Rolle als zusätzliche Hilfe nutzen möchten.</p>

  <div class="entry-details-stack reveal">
    <details class="entry-details">
      <summary>
        <span class="entry-details-kicker">Geordnete Startvorschläge</span>
        <span class="entry-details-title">Wenn Sie lieber systematisch statt situativ einsteigen</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="entry-details-body">
        <ol class="path-list">
          <li class="path-item">
            <span class="path-num">1</span>
            <div class="path-body">
              <a href="/modul/1/" class="path-title">Erst verstehen</a>
              <p class="path-desc">Beginnen Sie mit Modul 1. Danach wird meist klarer, ob bei Ihnen eher Belastung, Beziehung oder konkrete Schritte im Vordergrund stehen.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-item">
            <span class="path-num">2</span>
            <div class="path-body">
              <a href="/modul/4/" class="path-title">Wenn Sie schon am Limit sind</a>
              <p class="path-desc">Beginnen Sie mit Modul 4, dann Modul 5 und Modul 8. Sinnvoll, wenn Ihre eigene Belastung gerade dringlicher ist als Grundlagenwissen. Wenn Sie zuerst nur kurz einordnen wollen, hilft dort gleich am Anfang die Standortbestimmung.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-item">
            <span class="path-num">3</span>
            <div class="path-body">
              <a href="/modul/3/" class="path-title">Wenn die Beziehung im Vordergrund steht</a>
              <p class="path-desc">Beginnen Sie mit Modul 3, dann Modul 4 und 5. Passt, wenn Nähe, Vertrauen oder Rollenverschiebung die grösste Frage sind.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-item">
            <span class="path-num">4</span>
            <div class="path-body">
              <a href="/modul/6/" class="path-title">Wenn Sie sofort konkret handeln wollen</a>
              <p class="path-desc">Beginnen Sie mit Modul 6. Gespräche, Grenzen, Kommunikation in Episoden und Krisenplan sind direkt anwendbar, ohne Grundlagenwissen vorauszusetzen. Wenn Sie stattdessen vor allem Kontakte, Materialien oder rechtliche Orientierung suchen, gehen Sie zu Modul 8.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="path-item">
            <span class="path-num">5</span>
            <div class="path-body">
              <a href="/modul/2/" class="path-title">Wenn Sie verstehen wollen, was gerade mit Ihnen passiert</a>
              <p class="path-desc">Beginnen Sie mit Modul 2. Hypervigilanz, emotionale Erschöpfung, Suizidangst — für Angehörige, die die eigenen Reaktionen einordnen wollen.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="entry-details">
      <summary>
        <span class="entry-details-kicker">Nach Rolle</span>
        <span class="entry-details-title">Wenn Ihre Rolle zusätzliche Orientierung gibt</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="entry-details-body">
        <div class="modules-grid modules-grid--roles">
          <div class="module-card module-card--role role-card">
            <span class="module-number">Partner*in</span>
            <h3>Wenn Sie mitten im gemeinsamen Alltag stehen</h3>
            <p>Beziehung, Rollenverschiebung, Grenzen, Krisenplan und Kommunikation stehen oft früh im Vordergrund.</p>
            <div class="role-starts">
              <div class="role-starts-label">Sinnvolle Einstiege</div>
              <div class="role-start-links">
                <a href="/modul/1/" class="role-start-link">Modul 1: Verstehen</a>
                <a href="/modul/3/" class="role-start-link">Modul 3: Beziehung</a>
                <a href="/modul/6/" class="role-start-link">Modul 6: Konkrete Schritte</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

